Revision history for Perl extension Lingua::Conlang::Numbers

0.03  Mon Mar  8 20:47:35 EST 2010
    - added Esperanto POD translation -- forgot in 0.02

0.02  Sun Mar  7 18:45:23 EST 2010
    - added example.pl
    - replaced Module::Install with Module::Build
    - changed perl required from 5.10 to 5.8.1 (moriya/gardejo)
    - Esperanto
      + added support for a million through 999,999 vigintillion, long scale
      + added POD translation in Esperanto (moriya/gardejo)
    - Lojban
      + changed word separator from space to nothing
    - Toki Pona
      + changed mute/ale cutoff from 100 to inf (Matthew Martin)

0.01  Mon Mar  1 08:04:37 EST 2010
    - initial public release
    - includes Esperanto, Lojban, and Toki Pona
